post_text:
Thank you to the 113 people that have already designated Royalton Elementary PTO as their MORE Rewards School!

If you are not signed up or if you haven't designated Royalton Elementary PTO yet, it's easy to do.

1. Sign up for MORE Rewards at moreRewards.com or at any participating Coborn's, Cash Wise or Marketplace Foods store.
2. Designate Royalton Elementary PTO by logging in to your account at moreRewards.com or through the MORE Rewards mobile app.
3. Shop Coborn's, Cash Wise and Marketplace Foods stores for Food Club, Full Circle, Top Care, @ease, Paws & Tippy Toes brand products to earn points for your school. There are more than 3,000 qualifying items.
4. The points we earn will help grow our share of the $150,000 total. School Rewards funds can be used for whatever our school/organization needs.

Get started or learn more at https://www.morerewards.com/school

Thank you!!
